## DateRangePicker - Sélection Continue

### Structure du calendrier
Le fond bleu entre les dates doit être **CONTINU** (pas de gaps blancs).

```tsx
{/* Rendre par semaine pour avoir un fond continu */}
{weeks.map((week, weekIndex) => (
  <div key={weekIndex} className="relative flex">
    {/* Range background layer - bande bleue continue */}
    {hasRangeInWeek && (
      <div
        className="absolute inset-y-0 bg-[rgba(142,187,255,0.2)]"
        style={{
          left: hasStart ? `${startIndex * 48}px` : 0,
          right: hasEnd ? `${(6 - endIndex) * 48}px` : 0,
          borderTopLeftRadius: hasStart ? '4px' : 0,
          borderBottomLeftRadius: hasStart ? '4px' : 0,
          borderTopRightRadius: hasEnd ? '4px' : 0,
          borderBottomRightRadius: hasEnd ? '4px' : 0,
        }}
      />
    )}
    
    {/* Day cells */}
    {week.map((day) => (
      <button className={cn(
        "w-[38px] h-[39px] flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 mx-[5px]",
        isStart && "bg-[#1F1F9C] text-white rounded-l",
        isEnd && "bg-[#1F1F9C] text-white rounded-r",
        isToday && !isStart && !isEnd && "border border-[#5C5CB7] rounded text-[#5C5CB7]"
      )}>
        {day.date.getDate()}
      </button>
    ))}
  </div>
))}
```

### États des dates
- **Start date**: `bg-[#1F1F9C] text-white rounded-l` (arrondi gauche)
- **End date**: `bg-[#1F1F9C] text-white rounded-r` (arrondi droit)
- **In range**: Fond continu `bg-[rgba(142,187,255,0.2)]` sur la ligne
- **Today**: `border border-[#5C5CB7] rounded text-[#5C5CB7]`
- **Other month**: `text-[#CCCCCC]`

